      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>basmati rice</strong> and 175ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>cold</strong>&nbsp;<strong>water</strong> to a pot with a lid and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>\r\n<p>Once cooked, remove from the heat, remove the lid and leave the <strong>cooked rice</strong> to&nbsp;cool&nbsp;</p>",
